85 /** check sanity-check of voltage plausibility function
86  *
87  * limits may not be the same and must be ascending
88  */
89 void testAFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRangeLimitSanity(void) {
90  AFE_PLAUSIBILITY_VALUES_s limitsEqualValues = {
91  .maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV = 42,
92  .minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV = 42,
93  };
94 
95  AFE_PLAUSIBILITY_VALUES_s limitsDescendingOrder = {
96  .maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV = INT16_MIN,
97  .minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV = INT16_MAX,
98  };
99 
100  AFE_PLAUSIBILITY_VALUES_s limitsAscendingOrder = {
101  .maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV = INT16_MAX,
102  .minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV = INT16_MIN,
103  };
104 
105  TEST_ASSERT_FAIL_ASSERT(AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(0, limitsEqualValues));
106  TEST_ASSERT_FAIL_ASSERT(AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(0, limitsDescendingOrder));
107  TEST_ASSERT_PASS_ASSERT(
108  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(0, limitsAscendingOrder)));
109 }
110 
111 /** equivalence input classes for voltage check:
112  *
113  * cell voltage value:
114  * * in-range-value: e.g. 3500
115  * * out-of-upper-range-value: e.g. INT16_MAX
116  * * out-of-lower-range-value: e.g. INT16_MIN
117  * * just to be sure: 0
118  *
119  * limits:
120  * * negative values
121  * * positive values
122  * * zero
123  */
124 void testAFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(void) {
125  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(3500, testGenericLimits));
126  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_NOT_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(INT16_MAX, testGenericLimits));
127  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_NOT_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(INT16_MIN, testGenericLimits));
128  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(0, testGenericLimits));
129 
130  /* test around the upper threshold with #testGenericLimits */
131  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
132  STD_NOT_OK,
133  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
134  testGenericLimits.maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV + 1, testGenericLimits));
135  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
136  STD_OK,
137  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(testGenericLimits.maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV, testGenericLimits));
138  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
139  STD_OK,
140  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
141  testGenericLimits.maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV - 1, testGenericLimits));
142 
143  /* test around the lower threshold with #testGenericLimits */
144  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
145  STD_OK,
146  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
147  testGenericLimits.minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV + 1, testGenericLimits));
148  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
149  STD_OK,
150  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(testGenericLimits.minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV, testGenericLimits));
151  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
152  STD_NOT_OK,
153  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
154  testGenericLimits.minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV - 1, testGenericLimits));
155 
156  /* test around the upper threshold with #testGenericLimitsNegative */
157  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
158  STD_NOT_OK,
159  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
160  testGenericLimitsNegative.maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV + 1, testGenericLimitsNegative));
161  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
162  STD_OK,
163  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
164  testGenericLimitsNegative.maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV, testGenericLimitsNegative));
165  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
166  STD_OK,
167  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
168  testGenericLimitsNegative.maximumPlausibleVoltage_mV - 1, testGenericLimitsNegative));
169 
170  /* test around the lower threshold with #testGenericLimitsNegative */
171  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
172  STD_OK,
173  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
174  testGenericLimitsNegative.minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV + 1, testGenericLimitsNegative));
175  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
176  STD_OK,
177  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
178  testGenericLimitsNegative.minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV, testGenericLimitsNegative));
179  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(
180  STD_NOT_OK,
181  AFE_PlausibilityCheckVoltageMeasurementRange(
182  testGenericLimitsNegative.minimumPlausibleVoltage_mV - 1, testGenericLimitsNegative));
183 }

185 /** check if the function handles bad input from the API as expected */
186 void testAFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMaxBadInputFromAPI(void) {
187  TSI_GetMaximumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(50);
188  TSI_GetMinimumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(51);
189  TEST_ASSERT_FAIL_ASSERT(AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(0));
190 
191  TSI_GetMaximumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(50);
192  TSI_GetMinimumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(50);
193  TEST_ASSERT_PASS_ASSERT(AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(0));
194 
195  TSI_GetMaximumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(-50);
196  TSI_GetMinimumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(-51);
197  TEST_ASSERT_PASS_ASSERT(AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(0));
198 
199  TSI_GetMaximumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(51);
200  TSI_GetMinimumPlausibleTemperature_ExpectAndReturn(50);
201  TEST_ASSERT_PASS_ASSERT(AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(0));
202 }
203 
204 /** check if the function handles plausible and implausible input as expected
205  equivalence classes:
206  * below lower limit --> FAIL
207  * on lower limit --> PASS
208  * between lower and upper limit --> PASS
209  * on upper limit --> PASS
210  * above upper limit --> FAIL
211  */
212 void testAFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMaxVerify(void) {
213  const int16_t upperLimit_ddegC = 100;
214  const int16_t lowerLimit_ddegC = -10;
215  TSI_GetMaximumPlausibleTemperature_IgnoreAndReturn(upperLimit_ddegC);
216  TSI_GetMinimumPlausibleTemperature_IgnoreAndReturn(lowerLimit_ddegC);
217 
218  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_NOT_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(INT16_MIN));
219  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_NOT_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(lowerLimit_ddegC - 1));
220  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(lowerLimit_ddegC));
221  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax((lowerLimit_ddegC + upperLimit_ddegC) / 2));
222  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(upperLimit_ddegC));
223  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_NOT_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(upperLimit_ddegC + 1));
224  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(STD_NOT_OK, AFE_PlausibilityCheckTempMinMax(INT16_MAX));
225 }
